query: SELECT p.id, p.userId, p.title, p.totalPages, p.processedPages, COUNT(pg.id) as actual_pages FROM projects p LEFT JOIN pages pg ON p.id = pg.projectId GROUP BY p.id HAVING actual_pages > 0;
